#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:24
msgid "About"
msgstr "Rakenduse teave"

#. Voting
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:30
msgid "Do not participate in Station voting"
msgstr "Ära osale jaamade hääletuses"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:32
msgid ""
"If checked, your starred and streamed stations will not be used to calculate "
"the Station index popularity vote, nor the popular and trending stations"
msgstr ""
"Selle valiku eelistamisel lemmikuks märgitud ja voogedastatud "
"veebiraadiojaamad ei lähe arvesse ei jaamade populaarsusindeksi ega "
"populaarsust koguvate ja trendikate jaamade arvestuses"

#. Theme
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:38
msgid "System"
msgstr "Süsteemi määratud"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:39
msgid "Light mode"
msgstr "Hele kujundus"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:40
msgid "Dark mode"
msgstr "Tume kujundus"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:47
msgid "Theme"
msgstr "Kujundus"

#. Autoplay
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:52
msgid "Auto-play last station on startup"
msgstr "Käivitamisel alusta viimatikuulatud jaama esitamist"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:54
msgid ""
"If enabled, when Tuner starts it will automatically start to play the last "
"played station"
msgstr ""
"Selle valiku eelistamisel Tuneri avamisel jätkub viimatikuulatud jaama "
"kuulamine"

#. Restart Playing after network interuption
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:60
msgid "Restart playing after a network outage"
msgstr "Jätka taasesitust peale võrguühenduse katkestust"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:62
msgid ""
"If enabled, Tuner will restart playing the current station if it was stopped "
"by a network outage"
msgstr ""
"Kui see eelistus on kasutusel, siis Tuner jätkab peale võrguühenduse "
"katkestust viimase raadiojaama voogedastuse esitamist"

#. Start on Starred
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:68
msgid "Open to Starred Stations"
msgstr "Ava lemmikjaamade vaade"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:70
msgid "If enabled, when Tuner starts it will open to the starred stations view"
msgstr "Selle valiku eelistamisel Tuneri avamisel kuvatakse lemmikjaamade vaade"

#. Play Display
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:76
msgid "Show stream info when playing"
msgstr "Esitamise ajal näita meediavoo teavet"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:78
msgid "Cycle through the metadata from the playing stream"
msgstr "Töötle esitamisel oleva voogedastuse metateavet"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:82
msgid "Faster cycling through stream info"
msgstr "Voogedastuse metateabe kiirem töötlus"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:84
msgid ""
"Fast cycle through the metadata from the playing stream if show stream info "
"is enabled"
msgstr ""
"Kui voogaedastuse teabe kuvamine on kasutusel, siis selle eelistuse puhul "
"töödeldakse voogedastuse metateavet kiiremini"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:88
msgid "Stream metadata image popup"
msgstr "Hüpikaken voogedastuse piltidega"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:90
msgid "Show a movable popup with images discovered in the stream metadata"
msgstr "Näita liikuvat hüpikakent voogedastuses leiduvate piltidega"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:108
msgid "Language"
msgstr "Keel"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:109
msgid "Language changes restart Tuner"
msgstr "Keele vahetamisel Tuner käivitub uuesti"

#. end language selection
#. Export starred
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:117
msgid "Export Starred Stations to Playlist"
msgstr "Ekspordi lemmikjaamad esitusloendisse"

#. Import starred
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:127
msgid "Import Station UUIDs as Starred Stations"
msgstr "Impordi jaamade UUID-d lemmikaamade vaatesse"

